1
00:00:06,160 --> 00:00:07,970
[Lee Dong Won as Seung Jun]

2
00:00:07,970 --> 00:00:09,690
[Seong Tae as Jae Hyeon]

3
00:00:09,690 --> 00:00:11,430
[Shin Myeong Seong as Ho Yeon]

4
00:00:11,430 --> 00:00:13,110
[Kim Gyu Jong as Ju Won]

5
00:00:35,800 --> 00:00:43,800
[Happy Merry Ending]

6
00:00:48,959 --> 00:00:51,650
- Seung Jun!
- Hey, Seung Jun!

7
00:00:54,899 --> 00:00:57,642
- Let's go!
- Let go!

8
00:00:57,642 --> 00:00:59,625
I said let go.

9
00:00:59,625 --> 00:01:02,526
It's my turn now, and I'm not letting you go.

10
00:01:02,526 --> 00:01:03,934
Seung Jun!

11
00:01:03,934 --> 00:01:05,125
Stop this.

12
00:01:05,125 --> 00:01:08,825
If you don't come with me, he's not going to come out of this in one piece.

13
00:01:11,958 --> 00:01:13,484
He said no.

14
00:01:13,484 --> 00:01:15,442
Who do you think you're putting your hands on?

15
00:01:16,842 --> 00:01:19,134
- Son of a...
- Stop it.

16
00:01:22,692 --> 00:01:25,208
I don't know what it was like before,

17
00:01:25,208 --> 00:01:27,359
but now I'm not letting him go.

18
00:01:27,359 --> 00:01:30,389
Don't ever come near Seung Jun again, or...

19
00:01:32,459 --> 00:01:35,023
I'll make you regret it.

20
00:01:41,108 --> 00:01:42,760
Hey! Lee Seung Jun!

21
00:01:42,760 --> 00:01:45,710
Do you think he's any different? Hey!

22
00:01:49,942 --> 00:01:54,000
[Episode 7: The Temperature of Breakups]

23
00:02:06,310 --> 00:02:08,230
You should go now.

24
00:02:09,167 --> 00:02:11,500
I'll leave after I see you go inside.

25
00:02:13,809 --> 00:02:17,608
- Do you know why Kim Ju Won is doing this to me?
- What?

26
00:02:17,608 --> 00:02:20,334
Do you know why he stayed away all this while

27
00:02:20,334 --> 00:02:23,067
and decided to appear out of the blue?

28
00:02:24,651 --> 00:02:28,459
It's because you kept getting closer to me.

29
00:02:28,459 --> 00:02:30,559
I don't want to see either of you,

30
00:02:30,559 --> 00:02:32,925
so just go away.

31
00:02:33,708 --> 00:02:36,334
You shouldn't be alone right now.

32
00:02:36,334 --> 00:02:38,392
Why would you even want to be with me?

33
00:02:38,392 --> 00:02:39,892
Out of pity?

34
00:02:39,892 --> 00:02:43,267
Do you feel all grand and mighty when you're with someone like me?

35
00:02:43,267 --> 00:02:46,010
- It's not like that.
- Then what is the reason?

36
00:02:47,726 --> 00:02:50,392
I want to be there for you.

37
00:02:55,580 --> 00:03:00,692
That asshole and you are more or less the same.

38
00:03:00,692 --> 00:03:03,067
You both make my life difficult.

39
00:03:03,067 --> 00:03:05,451
- Seung Jun!
- Please.

40
00:03:05,451 --> 00:03:07,426
Leave.

41
00:03:08,417 --> 00:03:11,234
Leave me alone for God's sake.

42
00:03:12,918 --> 00:03:14,742
All right.

43
00:03:16,225 --> 00:03:18,042
I'll go.

44
00:03:31,726 --> 00:03:35,225
Showing him this side of me...

45
00:03:35,225 --> 00:03:38,457
was worse than seeing that jerk again.

46
00:03:44,140 --> 00:03:50,750
[One year later]
[SMB Production]

47
00:03:57,600 --> 00:04:00,350
I tried so hard to become a different person after that.

48
00:04:00,350 --> 00:04:02,875
Hello. I'm Lee Seung Jun, the composer.

49
00:04:02,875 --> 00:04:06,100
I sent you an email, and I was wondering if you got it.

50
00:04:06,100 --> 00:04:07,543
Please make sure to forward it.

51
00:04:07,543 --> 00:04:09,143
Yes.

52
00:04:23,860 --> 00:04:27,880
[02-514-397]

53
00:04:31,490 --> 00:04:33,234
Hello?

54
00:04:35,076 --> 00:04:37,250
Oh, yes, that's right.

55
00:04:42,782 --> 00:04:45,383
Yes, yes, I can do it.

56
00:04:45,383 --> 00:04:47,342
Thank you.

57
00:04:52,066 --> 00:04:55,683
And I began to change.

58
00:04:57,767 --> 00:05:05,667
♫ But even if I reach out my hand, I can't touch you ♫

59
00:05:07,059 --> 00:05:17,417
♪ I hope we can meet again outside of what exists in my memories ♪

60
00:05:17,417 --> 00:05:20,742
Yeon Oh! I think it's done.

61
00:05:20,742 --> 00:05:23,425
- Already?
- Yes, we've got it.

62
00:05:23,425 --> 00:05:25,129
You can come out.

63
00:05:25,129 --> 00:05:27,229
Thank you.

64
00:05:27,229 --> 00:05:28,767
- Isn't it good?
- It really is.

65
00:05:28,767 --> 00:05:30,267
Right?

66
00:05:34,492 --> 00:05:35,625
Was it okay?

67
00:05:35,625 --> 00:05:38,414
This song is going to be a total hit.

68
00:05:38,414 --> 00:05:41,716
- Thank you.
- No, no, it's all on you.

69
00:05:43,167 --> 00:05:45,659
Hi, hello, hi.

70
00:05:45,659 --> 00:05:46,934
Chan Wu!

71
00:05:46,934 --> 00:05:49,633
Hyeong! Congratulations.

72
00:05:49,633 --> 00:05:51,808
Are you done recording already?

73
00:05:51,808 --> 00:05:53,583
I knew you'd make it!

74
00:05:53,583 --> 00:05:55,585
It just ended. Thank you.

75
00:05:55,585 --> 00:05:56,917
Are you all right?

76
00:05:56,917 --> 00:05:58,891
I'm... good, I guess.

77
00:05:58,891 --> 00:06:01,800
I love working at the same company as you.

78
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:04,300
I can breathe easier, you know.

79
00:06:04,300 --> 00:06:07,051
I knew that asshole Kim Ju Won was going to go down.

80
00:06:07,051 --> 00:06:08,842
I mean, he shouldn't have messed with kids.

81
00:06:08,842 --> 00:06:12,658
I know, right? This is why you shouldn't judge a person by physical appearance alone.

82
00:06:12,658 --> 00:06:14,517
Well, it all worked out.

83
00:06:14,517 --> 00:06:18,393
Ugh... Just thinking about him makes me lose my appetite.

84
00:06:18,393 --> 00:06:22,167
Yeon Oh? Do you want to get some beef?

85
00:06:22,167 --> 00:06:25,058
Sorry, I've got plans.

86
00:06:25,058 --> 00:06:26,702
Okay.

87
00:06:30,558 --> 00:06:33,267
Im Ho Yeon, I'll take care of the rest.

88
00:06:33,267 --> 00:06:35,685
No, it's all right.

89
00:06:35,685 --> 00:06:38,035
Your lover is here... Go see him.

90
00:06:38,035 --> 00:06:40,560
Come on! I told you we are not dating!

91
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:43,571
- Get this cleaned up.
- Okay.

92
00:06:47,227 --> 00:06:50,060
How is work? Is it fun?

93
00:06:50,852 --> 00:06:53,235
I'm still getting used to it, I guess.

94
00:06:54,602 --> 00:06:57,602
You should thank me for everything.

95
00:06:58,517 --> 00:07:00,551
Yes.

96
00:07:00,551 --> 00:07:02,935
I'm most grateful to you.

97
00:07:11,810 --> 00:07:13,610
Seung Jun!

98
00:07:22,451 --> 00:07:24,568
Buy me dinner sometime...

99
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:28,843
Okay.

100
00:07:34,521 --> 00:07:37,263
I wonder what he's doing now.

101
00:07:38,308 --> 00:07:41,241
Who? Song Jae Hyeon?

102
00:07:42,077 --> 00:07:44,385
He's probably having dinner.

103
00:07:46,351 --> 00:07:49,052
If you miss him so much, you should go see him.

104
00:07:50,919 --> 00:07:53,935
Will he want to see me, too?

105
00:07:57,386 --> 00:08:01,160
Sometimes I can't tell if you're really clueless... or just pretending.

106
00:08:02,825 --> 00:08:04,660
Wait, no.

107
00:08:04,660 --> 00:08:07,227
You are definitely clueless.

108
00:08:10,117 --> 00:08:12,393
Go get him.

109
00:08:12,393 --> 00:08:14,960
Before it's really too late.

110
00:08:46,625 --> 00:08:49,134
Hello.

111
00:08:49,134 --> 00:08:50,686
Would you like to order?

112
00:08:50,686 --> 00:08:52,575
One hot Americano, please.

113
00:08:52,575 --> 00:08:54,216
Okay.

114
00:09:18,433 --> 00:09:22,161
Excuse me, Sir. We are about to close.

115
00:09:22,161 --> 00:09:24,920
Would you like it in a to-go cup?

116
00:09:24,920 --> 00:09:27,820
No, it's okay.

117
00:09:40,400 --> 00:09:42,417
Without him,

118
00:09:42,417 --> 00:09:45,942
all this would have been impossible.

119
00:09:45,942 --> 00:09:50,240
I started singing again so I could be confident in front of him.

120
00:10:02,142 --> 00:10:04,287
Are you nervous?

121
00:10:04,287 --> 00:10:05,562
You'll come with me, right?

122
00:10:05,562 --> 00:10:09,346
I dropped everything for you. Hurry up and get ready, we're going to be late.

123
00:10:17,283 --> 00:10:20,578
Now, it was terribly difficult to get this person to join us.

124
00:10:20,578 --> 00:10:24,245
But you guys know us, and we finally made it possible.

125
00:10:24,245 --> 00:10:26,974
It's his first time meeting the audience.

126
00:10:26,974 --> 00:10:28,786
Are you excited, Guys?

127
00:10:28,786 --> 00:10:29,895
Yes!

128
00:10:29,895 --> 00:10:32,536
That's nowhere near enough! Let me hear it! Are you excited?

129
00:10:32,536 --> 00:10:33,628
Yes!

130
00:10:33,628 --> 00:10:36,786
Great, there are so many fans waiting here.

131
00:10:36,786 --> 00:10:41,370
We now have around 26,000 viewers watching.

132
00:10:41,370 --> 00:10:46,578
And we have 20 lucky fans here who have been picked to join us.

133
00:10:46,578 --> 00:10:54,375
I think we ought to stop stalling, before we get cursed out.

134
00:10:54,375 --> 00:10:57,500
So let's get down to it.

135
00:10:57,500 --> 00:11:00,317
Here's the masked singer, the man from the video with 10 million views!

136
00:11:00,317 --> 00:11:04,595
I give you Yeon Oh. A big round of applause, please.

137
00:11:04,595 --> 00:11:06,661
Oh! Hello!

138
00:11:06,661 --> 00:11:09,170
Louder!

139
00:11:09,775 --> 00:11:12,328
Yeon Oh, hi!

140
00:11:12,328 --> 00:11:16,287
It's your first time meeting the audience, so please say hello.

141
00:11:16,287 --> 00:11:19,343
Hello, I'm Yeon Oh, a singer and songwriter.

142
00:11:20,458 --> 00:11:21,708
Yeon Oh!

143
00:11:21,708 --> 00:11:23,045
Forever!

144
00:11:23,045 --> 00:11:25,454
- Yeon Oh!
- Forever!

145
00:11:25,454 --> 00:11:28,067
Your fans shouted, "Yeon Oh forever."

146
00:11:28,067 --> 00:11:30,208
Here! Please take a seat.

147
00:11:30,208 --> 00:11:33,728
Now, we can see your song was released at 10 a.m. today,

148
00:11:33,728 --> 00:11:36,236
and it has shot up the charts quickly.

149
00:11:36,236 --> 00:11:38,703
Yes, I can barely believe it myself.

150
00:11:38,703 --> 00:11:43,911
I heard that this song was based on your own experiences.

151
00:11:43,911 --> 00:11:45,208
Yes, that's true.

152
00:11:45,208 --> 00:11:48,625
Now, a lot of people, myself included, must be wondering about that.

153
00:11:48,625 --> 00:11:53,121
Could you tell us your story in more detail here?

154
00:11:56,218 --> 00:11:59,059
When I had a severe panic disorder,

155
00:11:59,059 --> 00:12:01,717
I met that person for the first time.

156
00:12:12,830 --> 00:12:14,558
Wait...

157
00:12:16,812 --> 00:12:19,838
Do you want to have dinner together?

158
00:12:19,838 --> 00:12:21,588
I'll... I'll do it.

159
00:12:28,204 --> 00:12:32,538
Why are you being like this... to someone like me?

160
00:12:32,538 --> 00:12:37,604
I just want to stay by your side and protect you.

161
00:12:40,354 --> 00:12:42,080
Please.

162
00:12:42,080 --> 00:12:43,965
Leave.

163
00:12:45,058 --> 00:12:47,841
Leave me alone for God's sake.

164
00:12:49,662 --> 00:12:51,304
All right.

165
00:12:53,700 --> 00:12:59,438
That person must be really regretting not holding on to you right now, right?

166
00:12:59,438 --> 00:13:03,396
Now that we have you here, we have to listen to your new song.

167
00:13:03,396 --> 00:13:05,558
- Yeon Oh, are you ready?
- Yes, I am.

168
00:13:05,558 --> 00:13:09,543
Here's Yeon Oh's new title track, "Reaching Out to You."

169
00:13:09,543 --> 00:13:13,735
A big round of applause, please!

170
00:13:20,204 --> 00:13:27,604
♪ Quietly my two lips come together ♪

171
00:13:27,604 --> 00:13:33,760
♪ And call out your name ♪

172
00:13:35,096 --> 00:13:42,396
♪ Before I knew it, my empty days became filled ♪

173
00:13:42,396 --> 00:13:48,850
♪ With you and memories of you ♪

174
00:13:48,850 --> 00:13:56,187
♪ When I close my eyes, when the wind blows ♪

175
00:13:56,187 --> 00:14:03,470
♪ It feels as though you are right in front of me ♪

176
00:14:03,470 --> 00:14:12,796
♪ But even if I reach out my hand, I can't touch you ♪

177
00:14:12,796 --> 00:14:22,652
♪ I hope we can meet again outside of what exists in my memories ♪

178
00:14:26,630 --> 00:14:34,080
♫ Even if I call you softly ♫

179
00:14:34,080 --> 00:14:40,320
♫ With all of my heart ♫

180
00:14:41,560 --> 00:14:48,810
♫ The only thing in front of me would be a silent space ♫

181
00:14:48,810 --> 00:14:55,270
♫ It would be just another foolish sigh ♫

182
00:14:55,270 --> 00:15:02,830
♫ When I close my eyes, when the wind blows ♫
